<!-- Company Story Section -->
<div class="company-story-section py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
                <div class="story-image-container">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1470&q=80" alt="GrowTrack Team" class="story-image">
                    <div class="story-image-overlay"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="story-content">
                    <span class="section-badge">OUR MISSION</span>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Empowering Business Growth</h2>
                    <p class="section-text">
                        GrowTrack is a comprehensive digital platform designed to support the evolving needs of sellers and marketplace administrators. It aims to modernize the way SMEs operate by providing an intuitive interface for managing product listings, tracking sales performance, monitoring inventory levels, and generating insights through dashboards and reports.
                    </p>
                    <p class="section-text">
                        By bringing together various operational tools into a single system, GrowTrack enables SMEs to focus on growing their business while allowing administrators to maintain oversight and ensure compliance with platform standards.
                    </p>
                    <p class="section-text">
                        The system is intended to be scalable and adaptable, supporting both small-scale sellers and larger enterprises. With a modular design and role-based access, GrowTrack ensures that users interact only with the features relevant to their responsibilities, enhancing both security and usability.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

